:426404,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"其實係咪真係窮先住得公屋？"},{"pid":"eab876c00d85f6670c29296c4d649c1172d20a2c","tid":426404,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢仲留住間公屋比人笑啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好信埋晒啲都市傳說啦！以後見到公屋仔大聲笑尻佢地就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地自己知自己事 通常唔太敢講錢/投資/買車/買樓 都幾慘其實"},{"pid":"c20a335b10caca6207d515a2c55ef1d3f08af26f","tid":426404,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"因為我覺得香港咁發達城市 真窮人應該得好小"},{"pid":"be8313a9378e2a2cfb0955a70293af7e6b0ff697","tid":426404,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87c779af3a2453630495bbf78d363b15aeedfa53","tid":426404,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有錢仲留住間公屋比人笑啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好信埋晒啲都市傳說啦！以後見到公屋仔大聲笑尻佢地就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地自己知自己事 通常唔太敢講錢/投資/買車/買樓 都幾慘其實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見過啲公屋，周身名牌，又帶勞力士，有啲仲渣晒車咁，我心諗，你只係條公屋仔渣，學人充大頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當場問佢住邊，笑尻佢，再同佢講，你有錢買車，買勞，不如儲錢買樓啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依樣又真 好多倫敦金公屋仔就係咁樣"},{"pid":"544e7c7ba477a754f788b57e30ed8ae3057378a6","tid":426404,"uid":98840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"其實睇你點定義&quot;窮&quot;<br />\n如果買唔起樓已經算窮 咁香港有一半以上人都係窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba4a848b7c81abaa4d54f267d59471f19191a44","tid":426404,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2